      "content": "1.删除nginx，-purge包括配置文件\n\nsudo apt-get --purge remove nginx\n\n\n1\n\n\n2.移除全部不使用的软件包\n\nsudo apt-get autoremove\n\n\n1\n\n\n3.罗列出与nginx相关的软件并删除\n\ndpkg --get-selections|grep nginx\nsudo apt-get --purge remove nginx\nsudo apt-get --purge remove nginx-common\nsudo apt-get --purge remove nginx-core\n\n\n1\n2\n3\n4\n\n\n4.查看nginx正在运行的进程，如果有就kill掉\n\nps -ef |grep nginx\nsudo kill -9 XXX\n\n\n1\n2\n\n\n5.全局查找与nginx相关的文件\n\nsudo  find  /  -name  nginx*\n\n\n1\n\n\n6.删除列出的所有文件\n\nsudo rm -rf file\n\n\n1\n\n\n7.重装nginx\n\nsudo apt-get update\nsudo apt-get install nginx\n\n\n1\n2\n\n\n8.测试nginx配置是否正确\n\nsudo nginx -t\n\n\n1\n\n\n9.nginx 重启\n\nsudo service nginx restart\n\n\n1\n",
      "normalizedContent": "1.删除nginx，-purge包括配置文件\n\nsudo apt-get --purge remove nginx\n\n\n1\n\n\n2.移除全部不使用的软件包\n\nsudo apt-get autoremove\n\n\n1\n\n\n3.罗列出与nginx相关的软件并删除\n\ndpkg --get-selections|grep nginx\nsudo apt-get --purge remove nginx\nsudo apt-get --purge remove nginx-common\nsudo apt-get --purge remove nginx-core\n\n\n1\n2\n3\n4\n\n\n4.查看nginx正在运行的进程，如果有就kill掉\n\nps -ef |grep nginx\nsudo kill -9 xxx\n\n\n1\n2\n\n\n5.全局查找与nginx相关的文件\n\nsudo  find  /  -name  nginx*\n\n\n1\n\n\n6.删除列出的所有文件\n\nsudo rm -rf file\n\n\n1\n\n\n7.重装nginx\n\nsudo apt-get update\nsudo apt-get install nginx\n\n\n1\n2\n\n\n8.测试nginx配置是否正确\n\nsudo nginx -t\n\n\n1\n\n\n9.nginx 重启\n\nsudo service nginx restart\n\n\n1\n",
